OL,4,CBernard Mongan: Failings by Army over
OL,5,Csoldier's death, report says
OL,6, An Army investigation into the
OL,7, unexplained death of a British soldier
OL,8, has identified serious failings in its
OL,9, duty of care.
OL,11,FThe decomposing body of Lance Corporal
OL,12,FBernard Mongan was discovered in his
OL,13,Fbarracks in Catterick, North Yorkshire,
OL,14,Fon 23 January last year.
OL,16,FHe had been missing for three weeks
OL,17,Fwithout anyone noticing.
OL,19,FThe Army said the delay in discovering
OL,20,Fhe was dead was "unacceptable and
OL,21,Fprofoundly regrettable".
